Top:
Analyze exam results and decide whether a bonus should be paid

Refinement 1:
1) Initialize program variables
2) Input the 10 exam results, count passes and failure
3) Display a summary of the exam results and decide whether a bonus should be paid

set pass counter to zero
set no-pass counter to zero
set student counter to 1

while counter is less than or equal to 10
  prompt the user for an exam result
  input the next exam result

  if the student passed
    increment pass counter
  else
    increment no-pass counter

  add one to student counter

display number of passes
display number of no-passes

if more than eight students passed
  Display "Bonus to instructor!"
